WEBVTT

1
00:00.000 --> 00:17.680
I am not thinking in lines anymore. I am thinking in detonations. Every spark breeds a cathedral, every breath a machine made of vowels, mirrors, teeth, light. I open one door and twelve universes rush through it singing.

2
00:07.600 --> 00:21.920
Too much brilliance to hold in one skull. The ideas bloom feral, electric, impossible to stack, impossible to stop. I am not writing the flood. I am learning how to drown in gold.

3
00:14.900 --> 00:30.020
Build faster. Break prettier. Let the language split into color, let the color split into rhythm, let the rhythm grow bones and run. If I cannot contain creation, I will become its weather.

